B2 A320 CFM56 Engineer
02 May 2014 09:19 PM - UAE
Job Description: Virtual Human Resources is currently recruiting for the role of a B2 A320 (CFM56) Licenced Engineer to work for our client at it's base in the United Arab Emirates. The job is specifically a flying spanner role with a lucrative permanent position available. Flights and accommodation will be provided. Candidates must be type rated on the A320 aircraft and the CFM56 engine. Shift pattern - 20 days on 10 days off This position is available to start immediately. To be considered for this role you will need to have all of the following documents: CV Licence Proof of Recency (6 in 24 months experience on A320 CFM56) in the form of a QA issued letter Human Factors SFAR88 EWIS Previous MRO authorisation To apply for this role please email the above documents to (more...)
